caption.body: A lot of thought goes into every last detail in our exhibitions. For our Catch our Style exhibition we created custom wallpaper to hang as the background for all our display cases. We took high-resolution photographs of patterns featured on the seats of a Pacific Southwest Airlinesâ€™ Boeing 727 from the 1970s. The seats were covered in an intricate floral pattern fabric evocative of the popular psychedelic designs of the flower-power counterculture of the late 1960s.Come check out other psychedelic details in our Catch our Style exhibition, on display, pre-security, in our Aviation Museum and Library, located in the International Terminal. The Aviation Museum and Library is open from Sunday through Friday, 10am to 4:30pm.
